        PUSH-[ :span.count total POP
      POP
      PUSH-( for PUSH-[ PUSH-[ k v POP stats POP
        PUSH-[ :div.stat-item
          PUSH-[ :span.label PUSH-( name k POP POP
          PUSH-[ :span.value v POP
        POP
      POP
    POP
  POP-ALL
